author: Aramide Tinubu For Dailymail.Com
title: Woman sparks Twitter debate over frosted sugar cookies | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad 'Absolute garbage' or 'the god of all cookies'? Woman sparks heated Twitter debate after voicing disgust for frosted supermarket sugar cookies Taylor Haugen, 21, sparked a fierce debate on Twitter over her disdain for frosted covered sugar cookies like those often sold in grocery store bakeries Twitter users responded to Taylor immediately, either agreeing with her assessment of the 'flavorless' cookies or viciously calling her out Taylor has said she never wanted to cause WWIII, but she will never change her opinion about the cookies Published: 20:46 GMT, 17 February 2017 | Updated: 20:51 GMT, 17 February 2017 66 shares
